# Example repo list for scripts/pull-repos.sh
#
# One absolute path per line. Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are
# ignored. List every code repository this wiki tracks — a single repo for a
# monorepo project, or several for a multi-repo one.
#
# Copy this file to repos.txt at the repo root (which is what pull-repos.sh
# reads by default, and which is gitignored since the paths are machine-local).
#
# /Users/you/workspace/project/service-a
# /Users/you/workspace/project/service-b
